---
// Sección de servicios destacados con diseño moderno y atractivo
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-30 animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-80 h-80 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-30 animate-pulse"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header de la sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        Servicios Profesionales
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 font-heading">
        Especialistas en
        <span class="block text-primary-600">Costura y Bordados</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Más de 15 años perfeccionando nuestro arte. Desde uniformes escolares hasta bordados empresariales, 
        transformamos ideas en piezas únicas con calidad profesional.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de servicios -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Bordados Empresariales -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-3xl transform rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-2 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bordados Empresariales</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Personalización profesional para uniformes corporativos, promocionales y eventos especiales. 
            Diseños únicos que reflejan la identidad de tu empresa.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Logos y diseños personalizados
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Hilos de alta calidad y durabilidad
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Entrega rápida para pedidos corporativos
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/servicios/bordados-empresariales" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors">
            Conocer más
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Uniformes Escolares -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 rounded-3xl transform -rotate-1 group-hover:-rotate-2 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Uniformes Escolares</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Confección completa de uniformes escolares con los más altos estándares de calidad. 
            Diseños cómodos y duraderos para estudiantes de todas las edades.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Telas certificadas y resistentes
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Diseños ergonómicos y cómodos
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Talleres especiales por colegio
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/servicios/uniformes-escolares" class="inline-flex items-center text-secondary-600 font-semibold hover:text-secondary-700 transition-colors">
            Conocer más
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Polerones Cuarto Medio -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-3xl transform rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-2 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Polerones 4to Medio</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Diseños únicos para la graduación más especial. Polerones personalizados que capturan 
            la esencia de cada generación con calidad premium y estilo único.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Diseños 100% personalizados
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Múltiples opciones de bordado
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Materiales premium y duraderos
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/productos/polerones-cuarto-medio" class="inline-flex items-center text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:text-indigo-700 transition-colors">
            Conocer más
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA final -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a
          href="/contacto"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 text-white font-semibold text-lg rounded-xl hover:from-primary-700 hover:to-primary-800 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
          </svg>
          Solicitar Cotización Gratuita
        </a>
        
        <a
          href="/servicios"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-primary-600 text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300"
        >
          Ver Todos los Servicios
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>